HEADWORD: Hepato-pancreas
<hw>Hep"a*to-pan"cre*as</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>"h^par</grk>, <grk>"h`patos</grk>, the liver + E.
<ets>pancreas</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A digestive gland in
